cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting maxMIMO_layers to an out-of-range value of 10 will cause configuration validation failure as the maximum supported MIMO layers is typically 8 or less.
du.explanation_zh: 將 maxMIMO_layers 設定為超出範圍的值 10 會導致配置驗證失敗，因為最大支援的 MIMO 層通常為 8 或更少。
